Banks in Africa Key to Growth, Barclays Chief Writes in Times

-- B y   J o h n   S i m p s o n
-- 
2011-03-22T03:00:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-22/banks-in-africa-key-to-growth-barclays-chief-writes-in-times.html
Banks are often subject to
criticism in the developed world, but in  Africa  they are seen as
“an essential tool of economic growth,”  Robert Diamond , chief
executive officer of  Barclays Plc (BARC)  writes in the London-based
